document.topic_text: Colombari is an Italian surname. Notable people with the surname include: Enrico Colombari (1905–1983), Italian footballer and manager F. Colombari , Italian military officer and painter Martina Colombari (born 1975), Italian actress, model and television presenter This page or section lists people with the surname Colombari .
